    "title": [
      "[Crawling Shore, Promontory]"
    ],
    "description": [
      "Waves rage against the jagged stones of the promontory, sending up explosions of icy saltwater.  Crabs scuttle in the dark places between the stones, bright blue bodies starkly colorful against the monochrome of the black rock.  High tides have trapped kelp and other, more ambulatory sources of sustenance for the little crustaceans.  The finger of stone stretches defiantly out into the water, looking out onto a phalanx of vast icebergs."
    ],
